# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:12
translate chinese whitney0_24d01809:

    # "I walk down to the basement and check Dad's laptop."
    "我走下楼到地下室，查看爸爸的笔记本电脑。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:13
translate chinese whitney0_df4af9e8:

    # "There is a reply from Whitney."
    "有条来自惠特尼的回复。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:14
translate chinese whitney0_0e14f5d3:

    # "I take a deep breath and open the e-mail."
    "我深吸一口气，打开了那封邮件。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:17
translate chinese whitney0_7fb0886e:

    # "She would contact me soon, she says."
    "她说她很快会联系我。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:18
translate chinese whitney0_22c45920:

    # "I guess that's better than nothing. I don't have any other leads right now anyway."
    "我想这总比没有好。反正我现在也没有其他线索了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:19
translate chinese whitney0_0f12dd8e:

    # "I'll just have to wait and hope that she follows through with what she says."
    "我只能等待，希望她能信守承诺。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:22
translate chinese whitney0_4373f251:

    # "I send her a quick message back."
    "我迅速回了她一条消息。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:23
translate chinese whitney0_606df8e7:

    # "\"I'll wait, but don't take too long.\""
    "“我会等，但别拖太久。”"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:24
translate chinese whitney0_d972c5fe:

    # "Then I close the laptop and walk back upstairs."
    "然后我合上笔记本电脑，走回楼上。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:2
    old "First, you must clean the basement, then have Adrian unlock your dad's laptop, then tell Detective Rodriguez about what you found."
    new "首先，你必须打扫地下室，然后让阿德里安解锁你爸爸的笔记本电脑，接着把你的发现告诉罗德里格斯警探。"

    # game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:3
    old "hen you will be able to send Whitney an e-mail from your dad's laptop. After that, check the laptop again in a day or two to find Whitney's reply."
    new "这样你就能用你爸爸的笔记本电脑给惠特尼发邮件了。之后，过一两天再检查一下笔记本电脑，看看有没有惠特尼的回复。"

